safe that they don=E2=80=99t have to worry about them. Money in a bank acco=
unt simply=C2=A0<em>is money</em>; you don=E2=80=99t have to analyze your b=
ank=E2=80=99s financial statements before opening a checking account. The s=
hort-term senior debt of financial institutions is =E2=80=9C<a href=3D"http=
